## Next.js public environment variables

NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api/v1

## Supabase
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://jftggxxzqtmmqktvnlwc.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=replace-with-your-anon-key

## Admin
NEXT_PUBLIC_ADMIN_KEY=replace-with-admin-route-secret

## App
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_NAME=AgriculNet
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000

## Cloudinary (primary media storage + transformations)
## Create a free account at https://cloudinary.com/ and copy the cloud name from your dashboard.
## Then create an unsigned upload preset named "agriculnet_unsigned" under
## Settings -> Upload -> Upload presets.
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLOUDINARY_UPLOAD_PRESET=agriculnet_unsigned

